#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid "&plasma; Widgets"
msgstr "&plasma; vidinad"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid "Applets, or small applications that live on the desktop."
msgstr "Apletid ehk töölaual pesitsevad väikesed rakendused."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:89
#, no-c-format
msgid "<term>Containments</term>"
msgstr "<term>Konteinerid</term>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:91
#, no-c-format
msgid "Applets that act as the container for the &plasma; widgets"
msgstr "Apletid, mis toimivad &plasma; vidinate konteinerina."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:98
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On a default desktop, there are two main elements: the Panel and the Desktop "
"itself. Both are containments in the &plasma; sense."
msgstr ""
"Vaikimisi töölaual on kaks põhielementi: paneel ja töölaud ise. Mõlemad on "
"&plasma; tähenduses konteinerid."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:106
#, no-c-format
msgid "Default &plasma; Desktop"
msgstr "&plasma; vaikimisi töölaud"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:108
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &plasma; Desktop can be configured in countless ways. The screenshot "
"seen below shows a fairly standard desktop. Some distributions apply "
"extensive customizations, so your desktop may look different."
msgstr ""
"&plasma; töölauda saab igatmoodi seadistada. Allolev pilt näitab suhteliselt "
"standardset töölauda. Mõned distributsioonid kohandavad töölauda vägagi "
"palju, mistõttu sinu tegelik töölaud võib sellest pildist tunduvalt erineda."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:110
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Similarly, the graphical appearance of the interface elements can be styled. "
"These screenshots uses the &plasma; default style, Breeze."
msgstr ""
"Samuti saab stiilidega viimistleda liidese elementide visuaalset välimust. "
"Siinsetel piltidel on kasutatud &plasma; vaikimisi stiili Breeze."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:114
#, no-c-format
msgid "A fairly standard &plasma; Desktop"
msgstr "Üsna standardne &plasma; töölaud"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:146
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The program starter. Usually this will be <link linkend=\"panel-launcher"
"\">Application Launcher</link>."
msgstr ""
"Rakenduste käivitaja. Tavaliselt ongi see nimega <link linkend=\"panel-"
"launcher\">rakenduste käivitaja</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:147
#, no-c-format
msgid "A couple of icons giving easy access to often used applications"
msgstr "Mõned ikoonid, mis võimaldavad kiiresti pruukida levinumaid rakendusi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:149
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <link linkend=\"panel-taskbar\">Task Manager</link>, which shows the "
"titles of windows belonging to the applications currently running. No "
"application had opened a window, when the screenshot was taken"
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"panel-taskbar\">Tegumihaldur</link>, mis näitab parajasti "
"töötavate rakenduste akende tiitleid. Siinse pildi tegemise ajal ei ole "
"lahti ühegi rakenduse aken."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:150
#, no-c-format
msgid "The <link linkend=\"panel-system-tray\">System Tray</link>"
msgstr "<link linkend=\"panel-system-tray\">Süsteemisalv</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:151
#, no-c-format
msgid "The <link linkend=\"panel-digital-clock\">Digital Clock</link> widget"
msgstr "<link linkend=\"panel-digital-clock\">Digitaalkella</link> vidin."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:152
#, no-c-format
msgid "The <link linkend=\"panel-toolbox\">Panel Toolbox</link>"
msgstr "<link linkend=\"panel-toolbox\">Paneeli tööriistakast</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:153
#, no-c-format
msgid "The <link linkend=\"desktop\">Desktop</link> Toolbox"
msgstr "<link linkend=\"desktop\">Töölaua</link> tööriistakast."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:154
#, no-c-format
msgid "A Folder View widget, showing the content of the Desktop folder"
msgstr "Kataloogivaate vidin, mis näitab kataloogi Desktop sisu."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:161
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Panel"
msgstr "Paneel"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:163
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The default panel holds a few &plasma; widgets: starting from the left, "
"there is the application launcher."
msgstr ""
"Vaikimisi paneelil paiknevad mõned &plasma; vidinad: kõige vasakul asub "
"rakenduste käivitaja."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:167
#, no-c-format
msgid "Application Launcher"
msgstr "Rakenduste käivitaja"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:170
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Application launcher</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Rakenduste käivitaja</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:176
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Application launcher</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Rakenduste käivitaja</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:180
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can use it to start applications, open recently opened files and the "
"usual logout/shutdown options. There is also a structure that allows you to "
"browse through your applications. The layout has been optimized for the use "
"case that is most common: starting an application. The default tab is the "
"<guilabel>Favorites</guilabel> tab that holds the most-used entries. In the "
"beginning, you'll probably find yourself using the <guilabel>Applications</"
"guilabel> tab more often. Once you have found out what your most frequently "
"started applications are, <mousebutton>right</mousebutton> click on the "
"items and select the <guimenuitem>Add to Favorites</guimenuitem> to add them "
"to your <guilabel>Favorites</guilabel> (or directly into the panel or on the "
"desktop. Note that you need to <quote>unlock</quote> &plasma; by means of "
"<mousebutton>right</mousebutton> clicking on the desktop for any kind of "
"modification)."
msgstr ""
"Selle abil saab käivitada rakendusi, avada viimati avatud faile ning "
"mõistagi ka välja logida või arvutit sulgeda. Samuti saab selle abil kõiki "
"oma rakendusi näha. Selle välimust on optimeeritud, et see tuleks kõige "
"paremini toime kõige levinuma ülesandega, nimelt rakenduste käivitamisega. "
"Vaikimisi avatakse kaart <guilabel>Lemmikud</guilabel>, mis sisaldab kõige "
"enam kasutatud rakendusi. Algul läheb arvatavasti rohkem vaja kaarti "
"<guilabel>Rakendused</guilabel>. Kui oled üles leidnud rakendused, mida "
"kõige enam tarvitad, võid teha neil klõpsu hiire <mousebutton>parema</"
"mousebutton> nupuga ja valida <guimenuitem>Lisa lemmikute sekka</"
"guimenuitem>, mis lisab need kaardile <guilabel>Lemmikud</guilabel> (samuti "
"võib lisada otse paneelile, kuid pane tähele, et selleks peab &plasma; olema "
"<quote>lahtilukustatud</quote>, mida saab teha töölaual hiire "
"<mousebutton>parema</mousebutton> nupuga klõpsates)."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:196
#, no-c-format
msgid "Application Menu"
msgstr "Rakenduste menüü"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:198
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you prefer the traditional menu-style application launcher, change it by "
"<mousebutton>right</mousebutton> clicking on the menu button and selecting "
"<guimenuitem>Alternatives</guimenuitem>."
msgstr ""
"Kui eelistad tavapärast menüüpõhist rakenduste käivitajat, saab selle "
"valida, kui klõpsad hiire <mousebutton>parema</mousebutton> nupuga "
"menüünupule ning valid <guimenuitem>Alternatiivid</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:204
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Application menu</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Rakenduste menüü</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:210
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Application menu</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Rakenduste menüü</phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:217
#, no-c-format
msgid "Application Launcher Settings"
msgstr "Rakenduste käivitaja seadistused"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:219
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If you want to configure the application launcher, change it by "
#| "<mousebutton>right</mousebutton> clicking on the menu button and "
#| "selecting <guimenuitem>Application Launcher Settings</guimenuitem>."
msgid ""
"If you want to configure the application launcher, change it by "
"<mousebutton>right</mousebutton> clicking on the menu button and selecting "
"<guimenuitem>Configure Application Launcher</guimenuitem>."
msgstr ""
"Kui soovid seadistada rakenduste käivitajat, tee menüünupul klõps hiire "
"<mousebutton>parema</mousebutton> nupuga ja vali <guimenuitem>Rakenduste "
"käivitaja seadistused</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:224
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Application launcher settings</screeninfo>"
