#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:230
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Application launcher settings</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Rakenduste käivitaja seadistused</phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:237
#, no-c-format
msgid "Taskbar"
msgstr "Tegumiriba"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:239
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The taskbar is another widget on the panel. It shows an area for all open "
"windows on all desktops by default. You can make it show all open windows on "
"the current desktop only by checking <guimenuitem>Only show tasks from the "
"current desktop</guimenuitem> when you right click on the task manager, "
"between two windows. The size of the text on the taskbar items can be set in "
"&systemsettings; under the <menuchoice><guimenu>Appearance</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Fonts</guisubmenu> </menuchoice>. Right-clicking on the "
"taskbar brings the Settings dialog where you can choose several options to "
"customize your taskbar."
msgstr ""
"Järgmine paneelil paiknev vidin on tegumiriba. See näitab vaikimisi kõigi "
"töölaudade kõiki avatud aknaid. Selle võib panna näitama ainult aktiivse "
"töölaua aknaid, kui märkida valik <guimenuitem>Ainult aktiivse töölaua "
"akende näitamine</guimenuitem>. Selleks klõpsa hiire parema nupuga "
"tegumihalduril kahe akna vahel. Tegumiriba kirjete teksti suuruse saab "
"määrata Süsteemi seadistustes: <menuchoice><guimenu>Välimus</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Fondid</guisubmenu></menuchoice>. Paremklõpsuga "
"tegumiribal saab avada seadistuste dialoogi, kus on võimalik tegumiriba "
"mitut moodi kohandada."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:251
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here is a screenshot of the taskbar settings dialog"
msgstr "Tegumiriba seadistustedialoog"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:257
#, no-c-format
msgid "Taskbar settings dialog"
msgstr "Tegumiriba seadistustedialoog"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:265
#, no-c-format
msgid "System Tray"
msgstr "Süsteemisalv"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:267
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Another default panel item is the <application>System Tray</application>, "
"which is used by traditional applications and widgets as a dock. Right "
"clicking on the <application>System Tray</application> allows you to open "
"the settings dialog, where you can set entries to display and their "
"visibility."
msgstr ""
"Järgmisena paikneb vaikimisi paneelil niinimetatud "
"<application>süsteemisalv</application>, kus tavapäraselt asuvad "
"mitmesugused paneelile dokitud asjad. Paremklõps "
"<application>süsteemisalvele</application> võimaldab avada "
"seadistustedialoogi, milles saab määrata, milliseid ikoone üldse näidatakse "
"ja kas neid vaikimisi näidatakse või mitte."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:274
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>System Tray settings dialog</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Süsteemisalve seadistustedialoog</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:280
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>System Tray settings dialog</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Süsteemisalve seadistustedialoog</phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:287
#, no-c-format
msgid "Device Notifier"
msgstr "Seadmete teadustaja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:289
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "An icon located usually in the system tray is the <application>Device "
#| "Notifier</application>. Plug in a <acronym>USB</acronym> disk and a "
#| "dialog will open that allows you to open the device in &dolphin; or "
#| "another associated application."
msgid ""
"An icon located usually in the system tray is the <application>Device "
"Notifier</application>. Plug in a &USB; disk and a dialog will open that "
"allows you to open the device in &dolphin; or another associated application."
msgstr ""
"Ikoon, mis tavaliselt asub süsteemisalves, on <application>seadmete "
"teavitaja</application>. Ühenda arvutiga <acronym>USB</acronym>-pulk ning "
"ilmub dialoog, mis võimaldab avada seadme &dolphin;is või mõnes muus "
"asjakohases rakenduses."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:307
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The <application>Device Notifier</application> is used for handling "
#| "pluggable devices such as <acronym>USB</acronym> pendrives (also called "
#| "flash drives or thumb drives), digital cameras, external <acronym>USB</"
#| "acronym> hard drives, &etc; It also comes into play when a medium such as "
#| "a &CD; or DVD is loaded into an optical drive."
msgid ""
"The <application>Device Notifier</application> is used for handling "
"pluggable devices such as &USB; pendrives (also called flash drives or thumb "
"drives), digital cameras, external &USB; hard drives, &etc; It also comes "
"into play when a medium such as a &CD; or DVD is loaded into an optical "
"drive."
msgstr ""
"<application>Seadmete teadustajat</application> kasutatakse ühendatavate "
"seadmete haldamiseks, näiteks <acronym>USB</acronym>-pulgad (nimetatakse ka "
"Flash-pulkadeks või veel mõnda muud moodi), digitaalkaamerad, välised "
"<acronym>USB</acronym>-kõvakettad jne. Samuti kasutatakse seda juhul, kui "
"optilisse seadmesse sisestatakse mõni andmekandja, näiteks &CD; või DVD."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:309
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you plug in an external device, or load a new medium into a drive, the "
"<guilabel>Notifier</guilabel> window pops up (you can also open it "
"explicitly by clicking on its Panel icon.) It stays open while the cursor is "
"over it, otherwise it hides itself after a few seconds."
msgstr ""
"Välist seadet ühendades või uut andmekandjat seadmesse pannes ilmub "
"nähtavale <guilabel>teadustaja</guilabel> aken (selle saab ka otse avada, "
"kui klõpsata selle ikoonile paneelil). See jääb avatuks, kuni hiirekursor "
"selle kohal viibib, muidu aga peitub see taas mõne sekundi pärast."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:311
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Notifier</guilabel> window shows a list of all the devices it "
"currently knows about. Moving the mouse cursor over a device will highlight "
"how many possible actions are associated with that device."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Teadustaja</guilabel> aken näitab hetkel teadaolevate seadmete "
"nimekirja. Hiirekursori viimisel seadme kohale näeb, millised võimalikud "
"toimingud on antud seadmega seotud."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:326
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clicking anywhere in the shaded box around the device name (but not on the "
"eject/unmount icon if present) expands the entry to show the list of "
"possible actions for that device. The set of actions depends on the device; "
"it is configurable from the <application>Device Notifier</application>'s "
"context menu or from the &systemsettings; modules <ulink url=\"help:/"
"kcontrol/solid-actions/index.html\">Device Actions</ulink> and <ulink url="
"\"help:/kcontrol/solid-device-automounter/index.html\">Removable Devices</"
"ulink>. Simply select one with the mouse or keyboard to launch that action."
msgstr ""
"Klõps varjutatud kasti seadme nime ümber (aga mitte väljastamise või "
"lahutamise ikoonile, kui see on olemas) laiendab kirjet ja näitab selle "
"seadme korral võimalikke toiminguid. Need sõltuvad seadmest ning on "
"seadistatavad <application>seadmete teadustaja</application> "
"kontekstimenüüst või Süsteemi seadistuste moodulites <ulink url=\"help:/"
"kcontrol/solid-actions/index.html\">Seadmete toimingud</ulink> ja <ulink url="
"\"help:/kcontrol/solid-device-automounter/index.html\">Eemaldatavad seadmed</"
"ulink>. Vali lihtsalt hiire või klaviatuuriga mõni toiming ja see "
"käivitatakse."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:328
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There is also a small icon to the right of each entry showing whether that "
"device is currently accessible (or <emphasis>mounted</emphasis>) or not. "
"Only when a device is not mounted is it safe to physically disconnect it "
"from the computer. Clicking on the icon causes the device to be unmounted "
"and/or the medium to be ejected if it is currently mounted, and will mount "
"it if it is not. Note that unmounting/ejecting might fail if the device "
"still has open files on it, &eg; if a large file copy hasn't finished. In "
"most cases you can just wait a while and try again. When an unmounting has "
"succeeded, a success icon will be shown on the <application>Device Notifier</"
"application>'s icon."
msgstr ""
"Kõigist kirjetest paremal on lisaks väike ikoon, mis näitab, kas seade on "
"parajasti ligipääsetav (või <emphasis>ühendatud</emphasis>). Ainult siis, "
"kui seade ei ole ühendatud, on seda turvaline arvuti küljest füüsiliselt ära "
"võtta. Ikoonile klõpsates seade lahutatakse ja/või andmekandja "
"väljastatakse, kui see on parajasti ühendatud, või ühendatakse, kui see pole "
"veel ühendatud. Pane tähele, et lahutamine või väljastamine võib nurjuda, "
"kui seadmel on veel avatud faile, näiteks kui mõne suure faili kopeerimine "
"pole veel lõpetatud. Kui lahutamine õnnestus, näeb <application>seadmete "
"teadustaja</application> ikoonil õnnestumise ikooni."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:333
#, no-c-format
msgid "Hidden Items"
msgstr "Peidetud elemendid"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:335
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <application>System Tray</application> normally holds some more entries "
"like &klipper;, &kmix; &etc;"
msgstr ""
"<application>Süsteemisalv</application> sisaldab tavaliselt veel mõningaid "
"elemente, näiteks &klipper;, &kmix; jne."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:338
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Some of the default entries in the <application>System Tray</application> "
"are hidden to save space in the bar. To display these entries click on the "
"small white triangle <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"system-tray-up-arrow.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject>, then use the &LMB; to launch a widget or the &RMB; to "
"open its settings dialog."
msgstr ""
"Mõned <application>süsteemisalve</application> vaikimisi elemendid on ruumi "
"säästmise huvides peidetud. Nende nägemiseks klõpsa väikesele valgele "
"kolmnurgale <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"system-tray-"
"up-arrow.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></inlinemediaobject> ja "
"seejärel käivita vidin &HVNga; või ava selle seadistustedialoog &HPNga;."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:346
#, no-c-format
msgid "Digital Clock"
msgstr "Digikell"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:348
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The right-most &plasma; widget in the default panel holds the "
"<application>Digital Clock</application>. This clock can display the time in "
"different timezones as well as have its size changed. The clock will adjust "
"its font size to the area it is given by the surrounding containment (that "
"is the panel in this case). If you choose to display the date, this date "
"will be rendered using the <guimenuitem>Small font</guimenuitem> option from "
"the &systemsettings; <guilabel>Font</guilabel> dialog. The time will take "
"the rest of the space. So in the end, you'll choose yourself the amount of "
"information displayed, and if that fits. If you want to display more "
"information, make the panel larger or put the clock on the desktop where it "
"can grow freely."
msgstr ""
"Vaikimisi paneeli parempoolseim &plasma; vidin on <application>digikell</"
"application>. See võib näidata aega erinevates ajavööndites ja muidugi saab "
"selle suurust muuta. Kella kirja suurus kohaneb ümbritseva keskkonnaga, "
"antud juhul siis paneeli suurusega. Kui otsustad lasta näidata kuupäeva, "
"kasutatakse selle puhul <guimenuitem>väikest fonti</guimenuitem>, nagu see "
"on kindlaks määratud Süsteemi seadistuste dialoogis <guilabel>Font</"
"guilabel>. Ülejäänud ruum kulutatakse kellaaja näitamisele. Niisiis saad ise "
"valida, kui palju teavet näidatakse. Kui soovid näha rohkem teavet, suurenda "
"lihtsalt paneeli või aseta kell hoopis töölauale, kus selle suurus saab "
"palju paremini keskkonnaga kohanduda."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:364
#, no-c-format
msgid "Pager"
msgstr "Töölaua vahetaja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:366
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"An optional item on your panel is the <application>Pager</application>. It "
"allows you to switch between your virtual desktops. If you change the layout "
"of the <application>Pager</application> through the <guimenuitem>Number of "
"rows</guimenuitem> option, which will also affect the layout and animations "
"that are shown in &kwin;’s <guimenuitem>Desktop Grid</guimenuitem> effect. "
"For larger pagers, selecting <guimenuitem>Display windows icons</"
"guimenuitem> typically makes sense."
msgstr ""
"Paneelil võib samuti paikneda <application>töölaudade vahetaja</"
"application>. See võimaldab lülituda ühelt virtuaalselt töölaualt teisele. "
"Kui muudad <application>töölaudade vahetaja</application> välimust valikuga "
"<guimenuitem>Ridade arv</guimenuitem>, mõjutab see ka paigutust ja "
"animatsiooni, mida näidatakse &kwin;i <guimenuitem>töölauavõrgustiku</"
"guimenuitem> efekti puhul. Suurema töölaudade vahetaja korral on enamasti "
"mõttekas kasutada valikut <guimenuitem>Akende ikoonide näitamine</"
"guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:387
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Panel Toolbox"
msgstr "Paneeli tööriistakast"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:389
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If your desktop is unlocked (you can do that by <mousebutton>right</"
"mousebutton> clicking on the desktop, or when no application has the focus, "
"with <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>D</keycap></keycombo>, "
"<keycap>L</keycap>), a small &plasma; logo will appear in the bottom right "
"corner in the panel. Click on this toolbox, and the panel controller opens."
msgstr ""
"Kui töölaud on lahtilukustatud (seda saab teha hiire <mousebutton>parema</"
"mousebutton> nupuga töölauale klõpsates või kui ükski rakendus pole "
"fookuses, kiirklahviga <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>D</keycap></"
"keycombo>, <keycap>L</keycap>), ilmub paneeli alumisse parempoolsesse nurka "
"väike &plasma; logo. Klõps sellel avab paneeli seadistused."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:397
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Panel Settings</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Paneeli seadistused</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:403
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Panel Settings</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Paneeli seadistused</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:408
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The panel controller allows you to reposition, resize and realign the panel. "
"The &plasma; widgets living in this panel will adjust their size "
"automatically. &plasma; widgets have basic knowledge about sizing, provided "
"by the containment. They are programmed to take advantage of that size, and "
"inform the applet about how much space they possibly need. In the end, the "
"containment gives a possible size to the applets, the applets obey."
msgstr ""
"Paneeli kontrolleri abil saab muuta paneeli asukohta, suurust ja joondust. "
"Paneelil paiknevad &plasma; vidinad muudavad vastavalt oma suurust. &plasma; "
"vidinatele annab teadmise suurusest konteiner. Konteinerid on "
"programmeeritud suurust arvestama ning nad teavitavad aplette, kui palju nad "
"võiksid ruumi võtta. Niisiis, konteiner annab aplettidele teada nende "
"võimaliku suuruse."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:418
#, no-c-format
msgid "Adding Applets"
msgstr "Aplettide lisamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:420
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Unlock the desktop and you'll be able to add and remove &plasma; widgets "
"from panel or desktop. You add &plasma; widgets by simply dragging them "
"where you want them. <mousebutton>Right</mousebutton> click on an widget to "
"remove it. <screenshot> <screeninfo>Add Widgets</screeninfo> <mediaobject> "
"<imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"add-widgets.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </"
"imageobject> <textobject> <phrase>Add Widgets</phrase> </textobject> </"
"mediaobject> </screenshot> The <guibutton>Get New Widgets</guibutton> button "
"allows you to add widgets you've previously downloaded and download new "
"&plasma; widgets. Currently it supports native &plasmagik; packages and some "
"&Mac; OS&nbsp;X dashboard widgets. Widgets you install this way can then be "
"accessed just like regular, preinstalled widgets."
msgstr ""
"Kui töölaud on lahtilukustatud, saab paneelile või töölauale lisada &plasma; "
"vidinaid ning neid ka eemaldada. &plasma; vidinaid saab lisada ka neid "
"lihtsalt vajalikku kohta lohistades. Vidina eemaldamiseks tee sellel klõps "
"hiire <mousebutton>parema</mousebutton> nupuga. <screenshot> "
"<screeninfo>Vidinate lisamine</screeninfo> <mediaobject> <imageobject> "
"<imagedata fileref=\"add-widgets.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> "
"<textobject> <phrase>Vidinate lisamine</phrase> </textobject> </mediaobject> "
"</screenshot> Nupp <guibutton>Hangi uusi vidinaid</guibutton> võimaldab "
"lisada varem alla laaditud vidinaid ning alla laadida uusi &plasma; "
"vidinaid. Praegu on toetatud &plasmagik;i paketid ja &Mac; OS&nbsp;X "
"Dashboardi vidinad. Sel moel paigaldatud vidinaid saab kasutada täpselt nagu "
"kõiki teisi vidinaid."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:446
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Desktop"
msgstr "Töölaud"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:448
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The desktop is in fact another containment. One that does not put size "
"constraints on the applets. Applets can be moved and sized freely. On the "
"unlocked desktop, &plasma; widgets will show a frame when you move the mouse "
"over them. This applet handle allows you to move, resize, relocate and "
"realign the panel. It also allows you to drag &plasma; widgets on the "
"desktop. The buttons in the corner are used to resize, rotate configure and "
"remove the applet. When rotated, a &plasma; widget will act magnetic towards "
"12 o'clock, so it is easy to get them back into sensible position. By "
"default, most applets keep their aspect ratio when they are being resized. "
"If you want to freely resize an applet, hold the &Ctrl; key pressed while "
"resizing."
msgstr ""
"Töölaud on tegelikult samuti konteiner - selline, mis ei sea aplettidele "
"suurusepiiranguid. Aplette saab vabalt liigutada ning sama vabalt saab nende "
"suurust muuta. Lukustamata töölaual näeb &plasma; vidinatel raami, kui viia "
"hiir nende kohale. See võimaldab neid liigutada, nende suurust muuta, ümber "
"paigutada ja ümber joondada. Samuti võimaldab see &plasma; vidinaid "
"töölauale lohistada. Nurgas asuvate nuppudega saab apleti suurust muuta, "
"seda pöörata, seadistada või eemaldada. Pööramise korral käitub &plasma; "
"vidin, nagu paikneks ülasuunas magnet, nii et neid saab hõlpsasti "
"mõistlikusse asendisse tagasi. Vaikimisi säilitab enamik aplette suuruse "
"muutmisel proportsiooni. Kui soovid apleti suurust täiesti omatahtsi muuta, "
"hoia selle ajal all klahvi &Ctrl;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:461
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Right clicking on the desktop also offers you to configure aspects such as "
"the wallpaper and the layout used, and the mouse actions. It offers to "
"download new wallpapers through &knewstuff;."
msgstr ""
"Paremklõpsuga töölaual saab seda teataval määral seadistada, näiteks määrata "
"kasutatava taustapildi ja paigutuse ning hiiretoimingud. Samuti saab uusi "
"taustapilte &knewstuff;i abil."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:466
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On the <guilabel>Tweaks</guilabel> page you can configure to hide the "
"desktop Toolbox and adjust the widget handling."
msgstr ""
"Kaardil <guilabel>Trikid</guilabel> saab lasta töölaua tööriistakasti peita "
"ning täpsustada vidinate käitlemist."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:471
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Desktop Settings</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Töölaua seadistused</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:477
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Desktop Settings</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Töölaua seadistused</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:482
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To change the &plasma; theme or download a new one through &knewstuff; open "
"the <menuchoice><guimenu>Appearance</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Desktop Theme</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> page in the &systemsettings;."
msgstr ""
"&plasma; teema muutmiseks või uue allalaadimiseks &knewstuff;i vahendusel "
"ava Süsteemi seadistustes lehekülg <menuchoice><guimenu>Välimus</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Töölauateema</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:486
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "With open applications, it quickly gets hard to see the &plasma; widgets "
#| "on your desktop. The <emphasis role=\"bold\">Dashboard</emphasis> gets "
#| "those &plasma; widgets in front of you, much like the <guilabel>Show "
#| "desktop</guilabel> functionality you are used to from traditional "
#| "desktops."
msgid ""
"With open applications, it quickly gets hard to see the &plasma; widgets on "
"your desktop. The <emphasis role=\"bold\">Dashboard</emphasis> gets those "
"&plasma; widgets in front of you, much like the <guilabel>Peek at Desktop</"
"guilabel> functionality you are used to from traditional desktops."
msgstr ""
"Rakenduste avamisel muutub peagi raskeks näha töölaual paiknevaid &plasma; "
"vidinaid. <emphasis role=\"bold\">Dashboard</emphasis> toob need &plasma; "
"vidinad sinu silme ette samamoodi, nagu tavapäraste töölaudade puhul käsk "
"<guilabel> Näita töölauda</guilabel>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:496
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Folder View</title>"
msgstr "<title>Kataloogivaade</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:497
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Folder View</guilabel> widget is used to display entries like "
"folders or files from a folder, by default from <filename class=\"directory"
"\">$<envar>HOME</envar>/Desktop</filename>."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Kataloogivaate</guilabel> vidinaga saab nähtavale tuua mõne "
"kataloogi või kataloogi failid (vaikimisi on kataloogiks <filename class="
"\"directory\">$<envar>HOME</envar>/Desktop</filename>)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:500
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can choose to view either all files, or filter either by specific "
"regular expressions (&eg;, all files with a certain extension) or by file "
"type (&eg; just images)."
msgstr ""
"Seal saab valida, kas näidatakse kõiki faile või ainult mõningaid vastavalt "
"regulaaravamisele (&eg; faile teatava laiendiga) või tüübile (&eg; ainult "
"pilte)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:503
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This widget also supports basic file management properties (moving, copying, "
"cutting and pasting for example), and you can have as many as you want on "
"your desktop."
msgstr ""
"Vidin pakub ka lihtsamaid failihalduse võimalusi (näiteks liigutamine, "
"kopeerimine, lõikamine ja asetamine)."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:508
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Folder View</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Kataloogivaade</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:514
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Folder View</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Kataloogivaade</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:519
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you select the layout <guilabel>Folder View</guilabel> in the "
"<guilabel>Desktop Settings</guilabel> you can use one Folder View as the "
"whole desktop, effectively replicating the \"old style\" desktop paradigm."
msgstr ""
"Kui valid <guilabel>töölaua seadistustes</guilabel> paigutuseks "
"<guilabel>kataloogivaate</guilabel>, võid kasutada üht kataloogivaadet terve "
"töölauana, mis sisuliselt matkib \"vanaaja\" töölauda."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:525
#, no-c-format
msgid "&krunner;"
msgstr "&krunner;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:526
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&krunner; is a versatile mini command-line. You can use it to start "
#| "applications, open web pages, access bookmarks, search through your "
#| "desktop data, calculate short equations, and many more. Pressing "
#| "<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keysym>Space</keysym></keycombo> or "
#| "<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keysym>F2</keysym></keycombo> opens the "
#| "&krunner; dialog. You just start typing and &krunner; will start "
#| "searching matches as soon as you've entered more than two characters. You "
#| "can open the settings dialog to learn about &krunner;’s functionality, "
#| "provided by plugins. You can navigate through the matches using the tab "
#| "and arrow keys."
msgid ""
"&krunner; is a versatile mini command-line. You can use it to start "
"applications, open web pages, access bookmarks, search through your desktop "
"data, calculate short equations, and many more. Pressing <keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Alt;&Space;</keycombo> or <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;"
"<keysym>F2</keysym></keycombo> opens the &krunner; dialog. You just start "
"typing and &krunner; will start searching matches as soon as you've entered "
"more than two characters. You can open the settings dialog to learn about "
"&krunner;’s functionality, provided by plugins. You can navigate through the "
"matches using the tab and arrow keys."
msgstr ""
"&krunner; on väga mitmekülgne minikäsurida. Selle abil saab käivitada "
"rakendusi, avada veebilehekülgi, kasutada järjehoidjaid, otsida vajalikke "
"asju töölauaandmetest, arvutada lihtsamaid tehteid ja veel palju muud. "
"&krunner;i avamiseks vajuta <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;"
"<keysym>tühikuklahv</keysym></keycombo> või <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;"
"<keysym>F2</keysym></keycombo>. Hakka lihtsalt kirjutama ning &krunner; "
"hakkab kohe, kui oled sisestanud vähemalt kaks märki, otsima vasteid. Soovi "
"korral võid avada seadistustedialoogi, kus saab tundma õppida &krunner;i "
"arvukaid võimalusi, mida pakuvad vastavad pluginad. Leitud vastete vahel "
"võib liikuda tabeldusklahvi ja nooleklahvide abil."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:539
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&krunner; dialog</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&krunner;i dialoog</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:545
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&krunner; dialog</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&krunner;i dialoog</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:550
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Use the <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"krunner-"
#| "configure.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></inlinemediaobject> "
#| "button to open the <guilabel>Plasma Search</guilabel> &systemsettings; "
#| "module and configure where and what to search for in &krunner;"
msgid ""
"Use the <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"krunner-"
"configure.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></inlinemediaobject> button "
"to open the <guilabel>KRunner</guilabel> &systemsettings; module and "
"configure where and what to search for in &krunner;."
msgstr ""
"Nupuga <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"krunner-"
"configure.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></inlinemediaobject> saab "
"avada <guilabel>Plasma otsingu</guilabel> Süsteemi seadistuste mooduli ja "
"seadistada, kus ja mida &krunner;is otsida."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:555
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&krunner; supports <quote>Desktop Actions</quote> which are additional "
"actions an application can offer to perform common actions or jump directly "
"to a certain task from Task Manager. Common examples are <guilabel>Open New "
"Incognito Window</guilabel> to open your browser directly in private mode, "
"<guilabel>Compose Email</guilabel> without launching the full-fledged email "
"client first or the actions provided by &spectacle;:"
msgstr ""
"&krunner; toetab <quote>töölauatoiminguid</quote> ehk lisatoiminguid, mida "
"rakendused pakuvad teatavate ühiste toimingute sooritamiseks või mis "
"liiguvad otsekohe teatavale ülesannete halduri tegumile. Levinud näitekd on "
"<guilabel>Ava uus inkognito aken</guilabel> oma brauseri akna avamiseks kohe "
"inkognito-režiimis, <guilabel>Koosta kiri</guilabel> ilma täiemahulist e-"
"posti klienti käivitamata või ka töölaua-pildistaja &spectacle; toimingud."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:563
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&krunner; Desktop Actions</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&krunner;i töölauatoimingud</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:569
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&krunner; Desktop Actions</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&krunner;i töölauatoimingud</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:574
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If you press the <keysym>Down</keysym> key in an empty &krunner; a "
#| "history of the recent entities is shown. After invoking a search result, "
#| "its query will move to the top, so repeatedly used commands never fall "
#| "out of the list."
msgid ""
"If you press the &Down; key in an empty &krunner; a history of the recent "
"entities is shown. After invoking a search result, its query will move to "
"the top, so repeatedly used commands never fall out of the list."
msgstr ""
"Kui vajutad tühjas &krunner;is nooleklahvi <keysym>alla</keysym>, näed "
"viimaste kirjete ajalugu. Otsingutulemuse kasutamisel liigub selle kirje "
"esiotsa, nii et sagedamini kasutatavad käsud jäävad alati nimekirja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:578
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Remove single entries from the list using the "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"remove.png\" format="
"\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></inlinemediaobject> button or clear the complete "
"history in the &krunner; settings."
msgstr ""
"Nupuga <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"remove.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></inlinemediaobject>  saab loendist eemaldada "
"üksikuid kirjeid, &krunner;i seadistustes aga puhastada kogu ajaloo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:583
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to know what is going on on your system, pressing <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Esc;</keycombo> gives you quick access to a list of "
"windows and processes, with options to monitor their output and kill "
"processes."
msgstr ""
"Kui soovid teada, mis sinu süsteemis toimub, kasuta klahve nupule <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Esc;</keycombo>, mille järel näed akende ja "
"protsesside loendit ning võid jälgida nende väljundit ja vajaduse korral "
"protsesse tappa."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:591
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Activities</title>"
msgstr "<title>Tegevused</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:593
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The desktop toolbox, accessed via the upper left corner has a button for "
"displaying your activities, of which &plasma; allows you to have more than "
"one. Basically, that is multiple desktop containments hosting multiple sets "
"of &plasma; widgets. Display the <quote>Activities</quote> bar, select one "
"of the predefined activities or choose <guilabel>Create Activity</guilabel> "
"to create a new containment, select your new containment and customize "
"suiting your taste. &plasma;’s activities and &kwin;’s desktop grid are "
"similar in that respect, but there is a fundamental difference. While "
"virtual desktop are used to group and organize windows, &plasma;’s "
"activities are used to group and organize &plasma; widgets. This way, you "
"can switch between activities and have relevant &plasma; widgets supporting "
"the task you are currently trying to accomplish. You can create a "
"<quote>Free time</quote> activity, with comic strips, a puzzle and other "
"&plasma; widgets, and a <quote>Work</quote> activity, with relevant "
"<acronym>RSS</acronym> feeds, calculator and calendar, for example."
msgstr ""
"Töölaua tööriistakastis, mida saab avada ülal vasakus nurgas asuva nupuga, "
"on muu hulgas tegevusi näitav nupp. &plasma; lubab kasutada enam kui üht "
"tegevust. Põhimõtteliselt on tegemist mitme töölauakonteineriga, milles "
"kõigis on oma &plasma; vidinate valik,. Ava <quote>tegevuste</quote> riba, "
"vali mõni valmistegevus või uue konteineri loomiseks <guilabel>Loo tegevus</"
"guilabel>, suundu uude konteinerisse ja kohanda seda oma äranägemise järgi. "
"&plasma; tegevused  ja &kwin;i töölauavõrgustik on selles mõttes sarnased, "
"kuid erinevad siiski põhimõtteliselt. Virtuaalsete töölaudadega saab aknaid "
"rühmitada ja korraldada, aga &plasma; tegevused võimaldavad rühmitada ja "
"korraldada &plasma; vidinaid. Sel moel saab tegevuste vahel lülituda, et "
"oleks kättesaadavad just need &plasma; vidinad, mida on mingiks otstarbeks "
"vaja. Võid näiteks luua tegevused <quote>vaba aeg</quote>, kus on koomiksid, "
"pusle ja muid huvitavaid &plasma; vidinaid, ning <quote>töö</quote>, kus on "
"näiteks <acronym>RSS</acronym>-vood, kalkulaator ja kalender."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:609
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To delete an activity, press the <guibutton>Stop Activity</guibutton> button "
"on <quote>Activities</quote> bar (press <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;"
"<keycap>D</keycap></keycombo> then <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;"
"<keycap>A</keycap></keycombo> to open this bar) then click the red 'X' (or "
"press <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>D</keycap></keycombo> then "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>R</keycap></keycombo>) and confirm "
"the deletion."
msgstr ""
"Tegevuse kustutamiseks klõpsa nupule <guibutton>Peata tegevus</guibutton> "
"<quote>tegevuste</quote> ribal (vajuta <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;"
"<keycap>D</keycap></keycombo> ja siis <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;"
"<keycap>A</keycap></keycombo> riba avamiseks), siis klõpsa punasele 'X' (või "
"vajuta <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>D</keycap></keycombo> ja siis "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>R</keycap></keycombo>) ja kinnita "
"kustutamissoovi."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:622
#, no-c-format
msgid "Shortcuts"
msgstr "Kiirklahvid"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:624
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Most of &plasma;’s functionality is also accessible through keyboard "
"shortcuts. The various combinations should be pressed in sequence, that is "
"for example <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>D</keycap></keycombo>, "
"<keycap>A</keycap> means: Press &Alt; and <keycap>D</keycap>, release and "
"press <keycap>A</keycap>."
msgstr ""
"Enamikku &plasma; võimalusi saab kasutada ka kiirklahvidega. Eri "
"kombinatsioone tuleb vajutada üksteise järel, näiteks <keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>D</keycap></keycombo>, <keycap>A</keycap> tähendab: "
"vajuta &Alt; ja <keycap>D</keycap>, lase lahti ja vajuta <keycap>A</keycap>."

